f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d906513dab94494c709bc0f59bea28f6aaa7bb56","tid":2334743,"uid":184509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00f2971bd0c1de4878e31e0176a826ee9cda9b42","tid":2334743,"uid":184509,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T13:26:04.000Z","msg":"本主題可能正在討論有關「自殺」的內容。<br />\n若你需要進一步協助，可致電以下求助熱線：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/help/suicide-crisis-helpline\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/help/suicide-crisis-helpline</a><br />\n<br />\n篇篇都見到呢篇煩膠野<br />\n到底邊個會真係求助<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T13:26:22.000Z","msg":"段"},{"pid":"0bc5cbb0804b4a41168b5cdb959803c818c23d54","tid":2334743,"uid":11022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T13:37:26.000Z","msg":"有時情緒唔係靠思想可以控制改變，做下運動食下自己鐘意嘅嘢，睇下YouTube 有趣嘅嘢，咁多網友支持你，世界好美好，將來可能搵到比爸媽更重要嘅嘢"},{"pid":"756bef15210dc3aa3210f921643e0af740da2059","tid":2334743,"uid":370010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T13:40:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0e0311b098310fabf23d789d511dcadde3cba98","tid":2334743,"uid":137230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T18:14:48.000Z","msg":"Hello巴打上水覆下我地好嗎"},{"pid":"38d86f3155120b9b9d2e905e5dc3db0ff3d031c6","tid":2334743,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b265b43a11a2cf63dff5e870d684361bf905479","tid":2334743,"uid":86083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T10:49:15.000Z","msg":"真係好掛住佢哋<br />\n橫掂又無錢移民<br />\n都無咩將來<br />\n大家再見<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T15:56:10.000Z","msg":"或許我不能完全了解你內心的痛苦，但我也曾置身於無助和絕望之中，明白身處痛苦是怎樣一回事。無論你的是否想放棄自己，也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，因鬱結和壓力積存得太多太久，到情緒爆發時可能已超出你所能控制的程度。<br />\n<br />\n你不如停一停，到我們的網站  <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzM5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=25d6fd16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>  。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：下午4時至凌晨1時；星期六、日及公眾假期：晚上８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"d4392fcd411d91c204cd368301811c1905dad38a","tid":2334743,"uid":300424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T15:32:07.000Z","msg":"巴打 ，你點呀？"},{"pid":"d794c3f422fd19b82a210c8c275a794892eaf5ba","tid":2334743,"uid":156443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T15:44:54.000Z","msg":"Chat窿<br />\n俾次機會試下<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://chatpoint.org.hk/#/home\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchatpoint.org.hk%2F%23%2Fhome&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzM5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=7d8accb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://chatpoint.org.hk/#/home</a>"},{"pid":"afa62ed155f6f3c7dcd924fe8821a633fb42cc04","tid":2334743,"uid":170782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T15:45:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95cfcf5e5e8b6c64c6c17daeb1cf04e909cdb96a","tid":2334743,"uid":11022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T15:23:10.000Z","msg":"樓主覆下大家平安夜平安啦"},{"pid":"df8410bf0707df69b74e65417bbad0371f4f7545","tid":2334743,"uid":300424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T06:52:20.000Z","msg":"又唸起巴打， 希望你平安"},{"pid":"a5715f9d9c5bcf5129f46919c5022ef061344a2f","tid":2334743,"uid":300424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T14:59:13.000Z","msg":"巴打 今日天氣無咁凍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1e752d15417ff0aee9e2b0c596bb8daf606bc03","tid":2334743,"uid":2